<font color="#FF0000">RELATIVES OF THE KILLED </font><br>
<tt>Sun May 25  2:17:55 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I unfortunately was not able to meet one of my cousins as a result of the Viet Nam War.  He was ordered to the front lines a day or so after they touched base, he was blown away. Therefore, I do not have fond memories of Viet Nam because I never got a chance to meet him.  End of story.  Love, Janice Mason
